><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5551\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/df035776949905.5c78cfc7b3d0c.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1400\" height=\"935\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/df035776949905.5c78cfc7b3d0c.jpg 1400w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/df035776949905.5c78cfc7b3d0c-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/df035776949905.5c78cfc7b3d0c-768x513.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/df035776949905.5c78cfc7b3d0c-1024x684.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u00ec \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng, ph\u00e2n chia kh\u00f4ng gian theo phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng gian ch\u00ednh c\u00f3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e0i tr\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng. Kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ebd r\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eebng khu v\u1ef1c ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng ri\u00eang v\u00e0 ng\u0103n c\u00e1ch ph\u00e2n chia b\u1eb1ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh. V\u1edbi c\u00e1ch b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed n\u00e0y, t\u1eebng khu v\u1ef1c ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch t\u1eadp trung n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng di\u1ec7n t\u00edch nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5543\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/8a564776949905.5c78cfc7b4aae.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1400\" height=\"934\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/8a564776949905.5c78cfc7b4aae.jpg 1400w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/8a564776949905.5c78cfc7b4aae-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/8a564776949905.5c78cfc7b4aae-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/8a564776949905.5c78cfc7b4aae-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t Hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a kh\u00f4ng gian h\u01a1n l\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n \u0111\u1ecba v\u1ecb ti\u1ec1n t\u00e0i c\u1ee7a gia ch\u1ee7. Ch\u1ea5t ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00e2n chia th\u00f4ng minh, b\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd, tr\u00e0n ng\u1eadp \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng m\u1edf tho\u00e1ng. Song song \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch khai tri\u1ec3n m\u00e0u s\u1eafc. S\u1ef1 ti\u1ebft ch\u1ebf l\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc, gi\u00fap t\u00f4n b\u1eadt nh\u1eefng g\u00ec tinh hoa nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u1edbi gam m\u00e0u trung t\u00ednh ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 li\u1ec1n m\u1ea1ch trong m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian. C\u00e1c ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i c\u0169ng th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u00f3 k\u00edch c\u1ee1 v\u1eeba v\u1eb7n, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi n\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng g\u1ecdn xinh h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5550\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/cbd5fb76949905.5c78cfc7b5c90.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1400\" height=\"956\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/cbd5fb76949905.5c78cfc7b5c90.jpg 1400w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/cbd5fb76949905.5c78cfc7b5c90-300x205.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/cbd5fb76949905.5c78cfc7b5c90-768x524.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/cbd5fb76949905.5c78cfc7b5c90-1024x699.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e2n chia kh\u00f4ng gian kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn khi\u1ebfn c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng nh\u1ecf v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng, h\u00e3y t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c v\u00e1ch ng\u0103n k\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1eeba t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 ri\u00eang t\u01b0 v\u1eeba gi\u00fap kh\u00f4ng gian r\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi d\u00e0nh kho\u1ea3ng di\u1ec7n t\u00edch nh\u1ecf c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0y bi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft b\u1eb1ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t g\u1ecdn nh\u1eb9, th\u00f4ng minh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5546\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/74e23276949905.5c78cfc7b5a34.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1400\" height=\"923\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/74e23276949905.5c78cfc7b5a34.jpg 1400w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/74e23276949905.5c78cfc7b5a34-300x198.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/74e23276949905.5c78cfc7b5a34-768x506.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/74e23276949905.5c78cfc7b5a34-1024x675.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ph\u00e2n chia kh\u00f4ng gian kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t m\u00e0 c\u00f2n b\u1eb1ng ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n, v\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 ch\u1ecdn th\u1ea3m cho ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t kho\u1ea3ng ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng sinh ho\u1ea1t chung v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">S\u1ef1 ph\u00e2n chia kh\u00f4ng gian \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng m\u1ea3ng t\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o n\u00ean t\u1eeb \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. Khi s\u1ed1ng trong c\u0103n h\u1ed9 c\u00f3 \u01b0u th\u1ebf d\u00e0i v\u00e0 h\u1eb9p, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed c\u00e1c khu v\u1ef1c ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t theo chi\u1ec1u d\u1ecdc v\u00e0 b\u00e0i tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t theo chi\u1ec1u ngang. T\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t c\u00e1c khu v\u1ef1c ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng m\u1ea3ng t\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng gian th\u00eam d\u1ecbu d\u00e0ng, ti\u1ec7n \u00edch.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ph\u00e2n chia kh\u00f4ng gian b\u1eb1ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn l\u1ef1a m\u1ed9t khu v\u1ef1c c\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong kho\u1ea3ng di\u1ec7n t\u00edch r\u1ed9ng, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u1ea1o v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p sang tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i cho kh\u00f4ng gian nh\u1ecf.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Khi s\u1ed1ng trong c\u0103n h\u1ed9 c\u00f3 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch nh\u1ecf, gia ch\u1ee7 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed, thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf c\u00e1c ph\u00f2ng ra sao cho h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. V\u00e0 ph\u00e2n chia kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t theo phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn. V\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y,&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":5545,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[153],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4157","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-bst-vat-lieu-moi-2021"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4157","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4157"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4157\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/5545"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4157"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4157"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4157"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}